Package com.google.api.ads.dfp.lib

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AuthToken
    The AuthToken class creates an authentication token using the ClientLogin API.
    CaptchaInformation
    Represents CAPTCHA information retruned by the client login API.
    DfpHttpSender
    DfpHttpSender acts as a custom HTTP transport layer which allows for access to the MessageContext before it is processed.
    DfpService
    DfpService provides a class which defines a service that can be instantiated through reflection.
    DfpService.V201208
    The service class for v201208.
    DfpService.V201211
    The service class for v201211.
    DfpService.V201302
    The service class for v201302.
    DfpService.V201306
    The service class for v201306.
    DfpService.V201308
    The service class for v201308.
    DfpServiceFactory
    The DfpServiceFactory generates service stubs with an Axis EngineConfiguration which maps the HTTP transport to the class DfpHttpSender.
    DfpServiceLogger
    The class DfpServiceLogger allows logging of outgoing and incoming SOAP XML (DfpService) messages as API calls are executed.
    DfpUser
    The DfpUser class contains all needed information to authenticate a user as well as generate a valid service for that user.
    DfpVersion
    For each active version of the DoubleClick For Publishers API, there should exist a sub-class which implements the abstract class.
    ServiceAccountant
    The ServiceAccountant class acts as an accountant for metrics extracted from the request and response from a SOAP call.
    ServiceAccountantManager
    The ServiceAccountantManager manages all instances of ServiceAccountant by reference to the javax.xml.rpc.Service hashcode.
    ServiceAccountantRecord
    A record for purposes of metric accounting.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AuthTokenException
    An exception thrown when the ClientLogin API was unable to successfully generate a token.
